{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841344738,"sessionID":"ses_2879d0583ffeuS0IOdyWSENoec","part":{"id":"prt_d78647cb1001SpDBvHhOeadcDH","messageID":"msg_d78643c90001klTSzg6MwgRP8d","sessionID":"ses_2879d0583ffeuS0IOdyWSENoec","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_tool-dcfd79940be64a52953807d28843b9d1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md","newString":"## Constants\n\nThe `constants.go` file defines shared constants used across the API types.\n\n### Default Timeouts\n\n- **DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout**: `5m` - Default maximum execution time for code snippets\n- **SessionTimeoutDefault**: `15m` - Default timeout for idle sessions before cleanup\n- **MaxSessionDurationDefault**: `8h` - Default maximum allowed duration for a session\n\n### Runtime Types\n\n- **RuntimeTypePython**: `\"python\"` - Python runtime environment\n- **RuntimeTypeJavaScript**: `\"javascript\"` - JavaScript runtime environment\n- **RuntimeTypeTypeScript**: `\"typescript\"` - TypeScript runtime environment\n- **RuntimeTypeGo**: `\"go\"` - Go runtime environment\n\n### Protocol Types\n\n- **ProtocolTCP**: `\"TCP\"` - TCP protocol\n- **ProtocolUDP**: `\"UDP\"` - UDP protocol\n- **ProtocolSCTP**: `\"SCTP\"` - SCTP protocol\n\n### Default Resource Limits\n\n- **DefaultCPULimit**: `\"1\"` - Default CPU limit\n- **DefaultMemoryLimit**: `\"1Gi\"` - Default memory limit\n- **DefaultCPURequest**: `\"100m\"` - Default CPU request\n- **DefaultMemoryRequest**: `\"128Mi\"` - Default memory request\n\n### Seccomp Profile Types\n\n- **SeccompProfileTypeRuntimeDefault**: `\"RuntimeDefault\"` - Use runtime default seccomp profile\n- **SeccompProfileTypeUnconfined**: `\"Unconfined\"` - Use unconfined seccomp profile\n- **SeccompProfileTypeLocalhost**: `\"Localhost\"` - Use localhost seccomp profile\n\n## Validation Helper Functions\n\nThe `validation.go` file provides helper functions for validating common values:\n\n- **ValidateRuntimeType(runtime string) error** - Validates runtime type\n- **ValidateProtocol(protocol string) error** - Validates protocol type\n- **ValidateSeccompProfileType(profileType string) error** - Validates seccomp profile type\n- **ValidateTimeout(timeout *metav1.Duration) error** - Validates timeout duration\n- **ValidatePort(port int32) error** - Validates port number\n\n### Using Constants in Client Code\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nfunc createPythonInterpreter() *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter {\n    return &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Name:      \"python-interpreter\",\n            Namespace: \"default\",\n        },\n        Spec: v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n            Image:   \"python:3.11-slim\",\n            Runtime: v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython,\n            Timeout: &metav1.Duration{\n                Duration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n            },\n            Resources: &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{\n                Limits: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n                    CPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit,\n                    Memory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit,\n                },\n                Requests: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n                    CPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPURequest,\n                    Memory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryRequest,\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### Using Constants in Controller Code\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nfunc (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) applyDefaults(ci *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter) error {\n    if ci.Spec.Runtime == \"\" {\n        ci.Spec.Runtime = v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython\n    }\n    if ci.Spec.Timeout == nil {\n        ci.Spec.Timeout = &metav1.Duration{\n            Duration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n        }\n    }\n\n    if ci.Spec.Resources == nil {\n        ci.Spec.Resources = &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{}\n    }\n    if ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU == \"\" {\n        ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU = v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit\n    }\n    if ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.Memory == \"\" {\n        ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.Memory = v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit\n    }\n\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n### Using Validation Helper Functions\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nfunc validateCodeInterpreterSpec(spec *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec) error {\n    if err := v1alpha1.ValidateRuntimeType(spec.Runtime); err != nil {\n        return err\n    }\n\n    if err := v1alpha1.ValidateTimeout(spec.Timeout); err != nil {\n        return err\n    }\n\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n## Types\n\n### AgentRuntime","oldString":"## Types\n\n### AgentRuntime"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":22,"character":1},"end":{"line":22,"character":7}},"severity":2,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://staticcheck.dev/docs/checks/#S1023"},"source":"S1023","message":"redundant return statement"},{"range":{"start":{"line":52,"character":1},"end":{"line":52,"character":7}},"severity":2,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://staticcheck.dev/docs/checks/#S1023"},"source":"S1023","message":"redundant return statement"},{"range":{"start":{"line":88,"character":1},"end":{"line":88,"character":7}},"severity":2,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://staticcheck.dev/docs/checks/#S1023"},"source":"S1023","message":"redunda