me/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants_test.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation_test.go":[]},"diff":"Index: /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md\n===================================================================\n--- /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md\n+++ /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md\n@@ -7,8 +7,142 @@\n - **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n - **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n - **Kinds**: `AgentRuntime`, `CodeInterpreter`\n \n+## Constants\n+\n+The `constants.go` file defines shared constants used across the API types.\n+\n+### Default Timeouts\n+\n+- **DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout**: `5m` - Default maximum execution time for code snippets\n+- **SessionTimeoutDefault**: `15m` - Default timeout for idle sessions before cleanup\n+- **MaxSessionDurationDefault**: `8h` - Default maximum allowed duration for a session\n+\n+### Runtime Types\n+\n+- **RuntimeTypePython**: `\"python\"` - Python runtime environment\n+- **RuntimeTypeJavaScript**: `\"javascript\"` - JavaScript runtime environment\n+- **RuntimeTypeTypeScript**: `\"typescript\"` - TypeScript runtime environment\n+- **RuntimeTypeGo**: `\"go\"` - Go runtime environment\n+\n+### Protocol Types\n+\n+- **ProtocolTCP**: `\"TCP\"` - TCP protocol\n+- **ProtocolUDP**: `\"UDP\"` - UDP protocol\n+- **ProtocolSCTP**: `\"SCTP\"` - SCTP protocol\n+\n+### Default Resource Limits\n+\n+- **DefaultCPULimit**: `\"1\"` - Default CPU limit\n+- **DefaultMemoryLimit**: `\"1Gi\"` - Default memory limit\n+- **DefaultCPURequest**: `\"100m\"` - Default CPU request\n+- **DefaultMemoryRequest**: `\"128Mi\"` - Default memory request\n+\n+### Seccomp Profile Types\n+\n+- **SeccompProfileTypeRuntimeDefault**: `\"RuntimeDefault\"` - Use runtime default seccomp profile\n+- **SeccompProfileTypeUnconfined**: `\"Unconfined\"` - Use unconfined seccomp profile\n+- **SeccompProfileTypeLocalhost**: `\"Localhost\"` - Use localhost seccomp profile\n+\n+## Validation Helper Functions\n+\n+The `validation.go` file provides helper functions for validating common values:\n+\n+- **ValidateRuntimeType(runtime string) error** - Validates runtime type\n+- **ValidateProtocol(protocol string) error** - Validates protocol type\n+- **ValidateSeccompProfileType(profileType string) error** - Validates seccomp profile type\n+- **ValidateTimeout(timeout *metav1.Duration) error** - Validates timeout duration\n+- **ValidatePort(port int32) error** - Validates port number\n+\n+### Using Constants in Client Code\n+\n+```go\n+import (\n+    \"time\"\n+\n+    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n+    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n+)\n+\n+func createPythonInterpreter() *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter {\n+    return &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n+        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n+            Name:      \"python-interpreter\",\n+            Namespace: \"default\",\n+        },\n+        Spec: v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n+            Image:   \"python:3.11-slim\",\n+            Runtime: v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython,\n+            Timeout: &metav1.Duration{\n+                Duration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n+            },\n+            Resources: &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{\n+                Limits: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n+                    CPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit,\n+                    Memory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit,\n+                },\n+                Requests: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n+                    CPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPURequest,\n+                    Memory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryRequest,\n+                },\n+            },\n+        },\n+    }\n+}\n+```\n+\n+### Using Constants in Controller Code\n+\n+```go\n+import (\n+    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n+)\n+\n+func (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) applyDefaults(ci *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter) error {\n+    if ci.Spec.Runtime == \"\" {\n+        ci.Spec.Runtime = v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython\n+    }\n+    if ci.Spec.Timeout == nil {\n+        ci.Spec.Timeout = &metav1.Duration{\n+            Duration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n+        }\n+    }\n+\n+    if ci.Spec.Resources == nil {\n+        ci.Spec.Resources = &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{}\n+    }\n+    if ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU == \"\" {\n+        ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU = v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit\n+    }\n+    if ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.Memory == \"\" {\n+        ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.Memory = v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit\n+    }\n+\n+    return nil\n+}\n+```\n+\n+### Using Validation Helper Functions\n+\n+```go\n+import (\n+    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n+)\n+\n+func validateCodeInterpreterSpec(spec *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec) error {\n+    if err := v1alpha1.ValidateRuntimeType(spec.Runtime); err != nil {\n+        return err\n+    }\n+\n+    if err := v1alpha1.ValidateTimeout(spec.Timeout); err != nil {\n+        return err\n+    }\n+\n+    return nil\n+}\n+```\n+\n ## Types\n \n ### AgentRuntime\n \n","filediff":{"file":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md","before":"# AgentCube Runtime API\n\nThis package contains the Kubernetes API definitions for the AgentCube runtime resources.\n\n## API Group\n\n- **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n- **Kinds**: `AgentRuntime`, `CodeInterpreter`\n\n## Types\n\n### AgentRuntime\n\n`AgentRuntime` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a sandbox orchestration runtime for managing the lifecycle of agent pods.\n\n#### Spec\n\nThe `AgentRuntimeSpec` defines the desired state of an AgentRuntime:\n\n- **PodTemplate** (*SandboxTemplate, required): Template for creating sandbox pods\n- **SessionTimeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Timeout for idle sessions before cleanup (default: 15m)\n- **MaxSessionDuration** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum allowed duration for a session (default: 8h)\n\n#### Status\n\nThe `AgentRuntimeStatus` defines the observed state of an AgentRuntime:\n\n- **Conditions** ([]metav1.Condition, optional): List of conditions representing the runtime state\n- **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\n`CodeInterpreter` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a code execution environment for managing interpreter sandboxes.\n\n#### Spec\n\nThe `CodeInterpreterSpec` defines the desired state of a CodeInterpreter:\n\n- **Image** (string, required): Container image for the interpreter (e.g., \"python:3.11-slim\")\n- **Runtime** (string, optional): Execution environment type (default: \"python\")\n  - Allowed values: `python`, `javascript`, `typescript`, `go`\n- **Timeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum execution time for code snippets (default: 5m)\n- **Resources** (*SandboxContainerResources, optional): Compute resource requirements\n- **Env** ([]SandboxEnvVar, optional): Environment variables to inject\n- **EnabledPackages** ([]string, optional): Allowed packages for the interpreter\n\n#### Status\n\nThe `CodeInterpreterStatus` defines the observed state of a CodeInterpreter:\n\n- **Ready** (bool, optional): Whether the interpreter is ready to execute code\n- **Conditions** ([]metav1.Condition, optional): List of conditions representing the interpreter state\n- **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n\n### SandboxTemplate\n\nDefines the template for creating sandbox pods:\n\n- **Metadata** (*SandboxMetadata, optional): Labels and annotations for the pod\n- **Spec** (SandboxPodSpec, required): Pod specification\n\n### SandboxPodSpec\n\nDefines the pod specification for sandbox pods:\n\n- **Containers** ([]SandboxContainer, required): List of containers in the pod\n- **NodeSelector** (map[string]string, optional): Node selection constraints\n- **Affinity** (*SandboxAffinity, optional): Pod scheduling constraints\n- **Tolerations** ([]SandboxToleration, optional): Pod tolerations\n- **ResourceRequirements** (*SandboxResources, optional): Resource requirements for the pod\n- **Volumes** ([]SandboxVolume, optional): Pod volumes\n\n## Usage\n\n### Creating an AgentRuntime\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: AgentRuntime\nmetadata:\n  name: example-runtime\n  namespace: default\nspec:\n  podTemplate:\n    spec:\n      containers:\n      - name: agent\n        image: agent:latest\n        ports:\n        - containerPort: 8080\n```\n\n### Creating a CodeInterpreter\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: CodeInterpreter\nmetadata:\n  name: python-interpreter\n  namespace: default\nspec:\n  image: python:3.11-slim\n  runtime: python\n  timeout: 5m\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: \"1\"\n      memory: \"1Gi\"\n    requests:\n      cpu: \"250m\"\n      memory: \"256Mi\"\n  enabledPackages:\n  - numpy\n  - pandas\n  env:\n  - name: PYTHON_VERSION\n    value: \"3.11\"\n```\n\n### Using with client-go\n\n#### Creating an AgentRuntime\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nfunc createAgentRuntime(clientset *versioned.Clientset) error {\n    runtime := &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Name:      \"example-runtime\",\n            Namespace: \"default\",\n        },\n        Spec: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n            PodTemplate: &v1alpha1.SandboxTemplate{\n                Spec: v1alpha1.SandboxPodSpec{\n                    Containers: []v1alpha1.SandboxContainer{\n                        {\n                            Name:  \"agent\",\n                            Image: \"agent:latest\",\n                        },\n                    },\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    _, err := clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(\n        context.TODO(),\n        runtime,\n        metav1.CreateOptions{},\n    )\n    return err\n}\n```\n\n#### Creating a CodeInterpreter\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nfunc createCodeInterpreter(clientset *versioned.Clientset) error {\n    timeout := &metav1.Duration{Duration: 5 * time.Minute}\n\n    interpreter := &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Name:      \"python-interpreter\",\n            Namespace: \"default\",\n        },\n        Spec: v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n            Image:   \"python:3.11-slim\",\n            Runtime: \"python\",\n            Timeout: timeout,\n            EnabledPackages: []string{\"numpy\", \"pandas\"},\n        },\n    }\n\n    _, err := clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().CodeInterpreters(\"default\").Create(\n        context.TODO(),\n        interpreter,\n        metav1.CreateOptions{},\n    )\n    return err\n}\n```\n\n## Testing\n\nRun the unit tests:\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\n```\n\nThe test suite includes:\n- AgentRuntime type tests\n- CodeInterpreter type tests\n- Sandbox configuration tests\n- DeepCopy functionality tests\n- JSON serialization tests\n- Scheme registration tests\n\n## CRD Installation\n\nThe CRD YAML files are located at `config/crd/bases/`:\n\n- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`\n- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`\n\nInstall the CRDs:\n\n```bash\nkubectl apply -f config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\nkubectl apply -f config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n```\n\nVerify installation:\n\n```bash\nkubectl get crd agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\nkubectl get crd codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n```\n\n## Features\n\n### AgentRuntime\n\n- **Kubernetes-native**: Leverages Kubernetes CRD and controller patterns\n- **Type-safe**: Generated Go types for compile-time safety\n- **Extensible**: Supports custom pod templates, volumes, and configurations\n- **Status tracking**: Built-in conditions for runtime state management\n- **Resource management**: Support for resource limits, requests, and scheduling constraints\n- **Security**: Full support for security contexts, capabilities, and seccomp profiles\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\n- **Multi-language support**: Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Go runtimes\n- **Resource management**: Configurable CPU, memory, and ephemeral storage limits\n- **Timeout enforcement**: Maximum execution time for code snippets\n- **Package filtering**: Allowed packages for enhanced security\n- **Environment injection**: Custom environment variables support\n- **Status tracking**: Ready status and conditions for interpreter state\n\n## License\n\nCopyright 2024 Volcano Authors.","after":"# AgentCube Runtime API\n\nThis package contains the Kubernetes API definitions for the AgentCube runtime resources.\n\n## API Group\n\n- **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n- **Kinds**: `AgentRuntime`, `CodeInterpreter`\n\n## Constants\n\nThe `constants.go` file defines shared constants used across the API types.\n\n### Default Timeouts\n\n- **DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout**: `5m` - Default maximum execution time for code snippets\n- **SessionTimeoutDefault**: `15m` - Default timeout for idle sessions before cleanup\n- **MaxSessionDurationDefault**: `8h` - Default maximum allowed duration for a session\n\n### Runtime Types\n\n- **RuntimeTypePython**: `\"python\"` - Python runtime environment\n- **RuntimeTypeJavaScript**: `\"javascript\"` - JavaScript runtime environment\n- **RuntimeTypeTypeScript**: `\"typescript\"` - TypeScript runtime environment\n- **RuntimeTypeGo**: `\"go\"` - Go runtime environment\n\n### Protocol Types\n\n- **ProtocolTCP**: `\"TCP\"` - TCP protocol\n- **ProtocolUDP**: `\"UDP\"` - UDP protocol\n- **ProtocolSCTP**: `\"SCTP\"` - SCTP protocol\n\n### Default Resource Limits\n\n- **DefaultCPULimit**: `\"1\"` - Default CPU limit\n- **DefaultMemoryLimit**: `\"1Gi\"` - Default memory limit\n- **DefaultCPURequest**: `\"100m\"` - Default CPU request\n- **DefaultMemoryRequest**: `\"128Mi\"` - Default memory request\n\n### Seccomp Profile Types\n\n- **SeccompProfileTypeRuntimeDefault**: `\"RuntimeDefault\"` - Use runtime default seccomp profile\n- **SeccompProfileTypeUnconfined**: `\"Unconfined\"` - Use unconfined seccomp profile\n- **SeccompProfileTypeLocalhost**: `\"Localhost\"` - Use localhost seccomp profile\n\n## Validation Helper Functions\n\nThe `validation.go` file provides helper functions for validating common values:\n\n- **ValidateRuntimeType(runtime string) error** - Validates runtime type\n- **ValidateProtocol(protocol string) error** - Validates protocol type\n- **ValidateSeccompProfileType(profileType string) error** - Validates seccomp profile type\n- **ValidateTimeout(timeout *metav1.Duration) error** - Validates timeout duration\n- **ValidatePort(port int32) error** - Validates port number\n\n### Using Constants in Client Code\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nfunc createPythonInterpreter() *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter {\n    return &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Name:      \"python-interpreter\",\n            Namespace: \"default\",\n        },\n        Spec: v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n            Image:   \"python:3.11-slim\",\n            Runtime: v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython,\n            Timeout: &metav1.Duration{\n                Duration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n            },\n            Resources: &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{\n                Limits: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n                    CPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit,\n                    Memory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit,\n                },\n                Requests: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n                    CPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPURequest,\n                    Memory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryRequest,\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### Using Constants in Controller Code\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nfunc (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) applyDefaults(ci *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter) error {\n    if ci.Spec.Runtime == \"\" {\n        ci.Spec.Runtime = v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython\n    }\n    if ci.Spec.Timeout == nil {\n        ci.Spec.Timeout = &metav1.Duration{\n            Duration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n        }\n    }\n\n    if ci.Spec.Resources == nil {\n        ci.Spec.Resources = &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{}\n    }\n    if ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU == \"\" {\n        ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU = v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit\n    }\n    if ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.Memory == \"\" {\n        ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.Memory = v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit\n    }\n\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n### Using Validation Helper Functions\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nfunc validateCodeInterpreterSpec(spec *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec) error {\n    if err := v1alpha1.ValidateRuntimeType(spec.Runtime); err != nil {\n        return err\n    }\n\n    if err := v1alpha1.ValidateTimeout(spec.Timeout); err != nil {\n        return err\n    }\n\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n## Types\n\n### AgentRuntime\n\n`AgentRuntime` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a sandbox orchestration runtime for managing the lifecycle of agent pods.\n\n#### Spec\n\nThe `AgentRuntimeSpec` defines the desired state of an AgentRuntime:\n\n- **PodTemplate** (*SandboxTemplate, required): Template for creating sandbox pods\n- **SessionTimeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Timeout for idle sessions before cleanup (default: 15m)\n- **MaxSessionDuration** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum allowed duration for a session (default: 8h)\n\n#### Status\n\nThe `AgentRuntimeStatus` defines the observed state of an AgentRuntime:\n\n- **Conditions** ([]metav1.Condition, optional): List of conditions representing the runtime state\n- **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\n`CodeInterpreter` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a code execution environment for managing interpreter sandboxes.\n\n#### Spec\n\nThe `CodeInterpreterSpec` defines the desired state of a CodeInterpreter:\n\n- **Image** (string, required): Container image for the interpreter (e.g., \"python:3.11-slim\")\n- **Runtime** (string, optional): Execution environment type (default: \"python\")\n  - Allowed values: `python`, `javascript`, `typescript`, `go`\n- **Timeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum execution time for code snippets (default: 5m)\n- **Resources** (*SandboxContainerResources, optional): Compute resource requirements\n- **Env** ([]SandboxEnvVar, optional): Environment variables to inject\n- **EnabledPackages** ([]string, optional): Allowed packages for the interpreter\n\n#### Status\n\nThe `CodeInterpreterStatus` defines the observed state of a CodeInterpreter:\n\n- **Ready** (bool, optional): Whether the interpreter is ready to execute code\n- **Conditions** ([]metav1.Condition, optional): List of conditions representing the interpreter state\n- **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n\n### SandboxTemplate\n\nDefines the template for creating sandbox pods:\n\n- **Metadata** (*SandboxMetadata, optional): Labels and annotations for the pod\n- **Spec** (SandboxPodSpec, required): Pod specification\n\n### SandboxPodSpec\n\nDefines the pod specification for sandbox pods:\n\n- **Containers** ([]SandboxContainer, required): List of containers in the pod\n- **NodeSelector** (map[string]string, optional): Node selection constraints\n- **Affinity** (*SandboxAffinity, optional): Pod scheduling constraints\n- **Tolerations** ([]SandboxToleration, optional): Pod tolerations\n- **ResourceRequirements** (*SandboxResources, optional): Resource requirements for the pod\n- **Volumes** ([]SandboxVolume, optional): Pod volumes\n\n## Usage\n\n### Creating an AgentRuntime\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: AgentRuntime\nmetadata:\n  name: example-runtime\n  namespace: default\nspec:\n  podTemplate:\n    spec:\n      containers:\n      - name: agent\n        image: agent:latest\n        ports:\n        - containerPort: 8080\n```\n\n### Creating a CodeInterpreter\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: CodeInterpreter\nmetadata:\n  name: python-interpreter\n  namespace: default\nspec:\n  image: python:3.11-slim\n  runtime: python\n  timeout: 5m\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: \"1\"\n      memory: \"1Gi\"\n    requests:\n      cpu: \"250m\"\n      memory: \"256Mi\"\n  enabledPackages:\n  - numpy\n  - pandas\n  env:\n  - name: PYTHON_VERSION\n    value: \"3.11\"\n```\n\n### Using with client-go\n\n#### Creating an AgentRuntime\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nfunc createAgentRuntime(clientset *versioned.Clientset) error {\n    runtime := &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Name:      \"example-runtime\",\n            Namespace: \"default\",\n        },\n        Spec: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n            PodTemplate: &v1alpha1.SandboxTemplate{\n                Spec: v1alpha1.SandboxPodSpec{\n                    Containers: []v1alpha1.SandboxContainer{\n                        {\n                            Name:  \"agent\",\n                            Image: \"agent:latest\",\n                        },\n                    },\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    _, err := clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(\n        context.TODO(),\n        runtime,\n        metav1.CreateOptions{},\n    )\n    return err\n}\n```\n\n#### Creating a CodeInterpreter\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nfunc createCodeInterpreter(clientset *versioned.Clientset) error {\n    timeout := &metav1.Duration{Duration: 5 * time.Minute}\n\n    interpreter := &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Name:      \"python-interpreter\",\n            Namespace: \"default\",\n        },\n        Spec: v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n            Image:   \"python:3.11-slim\",\n            Runtime: \"python\",\n            Timeout: timeout,\n            EnabledPackages: []string{\"numpy\", \"pandas\"},\n        },\n    }\n\n    _, err := clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().CodeInterpreters(\"default\").Create(\n        context.TODO(),\n        interpreter,\n        metav1.CreateOptions{},\n    )\n    return err\n}\n```\n\n## Testing\n\nRun the unit tests:\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\n```\n\nThe test suite includes:\n- AgentRuntime type tests\n- CodeInterpreter type tests\n- Sandbox configuration tests\n- DeepCopy functionality tests\n- JSON serialization tests\n- Scheme registration tests\n\n## CRD Installation\n\nThe CRD YAML files are located at `config/crd/bases/`:\n\n- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`\n- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`\n\nInstall the CRDs:\n\n```bash\nkubectl apply -f config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\nkubectl apply -f config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n```\n\nVerify installation:\n\n```bash\nkubectl get crd agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\nkubectl get crd codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n```\n\n## Features\n\n### AgentRuntime\n\n- **Kubernetes-native**: Leverages Kubernetes CRD and controller patterns\n- **Type-safe**: Generated Go types for compile-time safety\n- **Extensible**: Supports custom pod templates, volumes, and configurations\n- **Status tracking**: Built-in conditions for runtime state management\n- **Resource management**: Support for resource limits, requests, and scheduling constraints\n- **Security**: Full support for security contexts, capabilities, and seccomp profiles\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\n- **Multi-language support**: Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Go runtimes\n- **Resource management**: Configurable CPU, memory, and ephemeral storage limits\n- **Timeout enforcement**: Maximum execution time for code snippets\n- **Package filtering**: Allowed packages for enhanced security\n- **Environment injection**: Custom environment variables support\n- **Status tracking**: Ready status and conditions for interpreter state\n\n## License\n\nCopyright 2024 Volcano Authors.","additions":134,"deletions":0},"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md","time":{"start":1775841344708,"end":1775841344735}}}}
