{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841360453,"sessionID":"ses_2879d0583ffeuS0IOdyWSENoec","part":{"id":"prt_d7864ba1c001Ak9Hrih8c490sr","messageID":"msg_d7864a43e0019cut2spr9OY10A","sessionID":"ses_2879d0583ffeuS0IOdyWSENoec","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_tool-ddb909b07e994c55a7a49c3905f3f926","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md","newString":"## Testing\n\nRun the unit tests:\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\n```\n\nThe test suite includes:\n- AgentRuntime type tests\n- CodeInterpreter type tests\n- Sandbox configuration tests\n- DeepCopy functionality tests\n- JSON serialization tests\n- Scheme registration tests\n- Constants tests (timeout, runtime types, protocol types, resource limits, seccomp profiles)\n- Validation helper function tests (runtime type, protocol, seccomp profile, timeout, port)\n\n### Running specific test suites\n\n```bash\n# Run only constants tests\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestDefault\n\n# Run only validation tests\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestValidate\n\n# Run all tests with verbose output\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v\n```","oldString":"## Testing\n\nRun the unit tests:\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\n```\n\nThe test suite includes:\n- AgentRuntime type tests\n- CodeInterpreter type tests\n- Sandbox configuration tests\n- DeepCopy functionality tests\n- JSON serialization tests\n- Scheme registration tests"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":22,"character":1},"end":{"lin