lid protocol: %s, must be one of: TCP, UDP, SCTP\", protocol)\n50: \t}\n51: \n52: \treturn nil\n53: }\n54: \n55: func ValidateSeccompProfileType(profileType string) error {\n56: \tif profileType == \"\" {\n57: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"seccomp profile type cannot be empty\")\n58: \t}\n59: \n60: \tif !validSeccompProfileTypes[profileType] {\n61: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"invalid seccomp profile type: %s, must be one of: RuntimeDefault, Unconfined, Localhost\", profileType)\n62: \t}\n63: \n64: \treturn nil\n65: }\n66: \n67: func ValidateTimeout(timeout *metav1.Duration) error {\n68: \tif timeout == nil {\n69: \t\treturn nil\n70: \t}\n71: \n72: \tif timeout.Duration <= 0 {\n73: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"timeout must be positive, got: %v\", timeout.Duration)\n74: \t}\n75: \n76: \tmaxTimeout := 24 * time.Hour\n77: \tif timeout.Duration > maxTimeout {\n78: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"timeout cannot exceed 24 hours, got: %v\", timeout.Duration)\n79: \t}\n80: \n81: \treturn nil\n82: }\n83: \n84: func ValidatePort(port int32) error {\n85: \tif port < 1 || port > 65535 {\n86: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"port must be between 1 and 65535, got: %d\", port)\n87: \t}\n88: \n89: \treturn nil\n90: }\n\n(End of file - total 90 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nvar (\n\tvalidRuntimeTypes = map[string]bool{\n\t\tRuntimeTypePython:     true,\n\t\tRuntimeTypeJavaScript: true,\n\t\tRuntimeTypeTypeScript: true,\n\t\tRuntimeTypeGo:         true,\n\t}\n\n\tvalidProtocolTypes = map[string]bool{\n\t\tProtocolTCP:  true,\n\t\tProtocolUDP:  true,","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation.go","time":{"start":1775841513149,"end":1775841513159}}}}
